{
    "pages": [
        {
            "chapter": 87,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "But you prefer the life of this world"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 87,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "although the Hereafter is better and more lasting"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 87,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "This indeed is what is taught in the former scriptures"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 87,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "the scriptures of Abraham and Moses"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "Have you heard about the Overwhelming Event"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "On that Day, there shall be downcast faces"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "labouring, weary"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "they shall enter a burning Fire"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "and will be made to drink from a boiling spring"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "they shall have no food but thorns"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "which will neither nourish nor satisfy hunger"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "Some faces on that Day will be radiant"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "well pleased with the result of their striving"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "in a sublime garden"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "where they will hear no idle talk"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "with a flowing spring"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "raised couches"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "and goblets set at hand"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "cushions ranged"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "and carpets spread out"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "Do they never reflect on the camels and how they were created"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "and on the sky, how it is raised aloft"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "and on the mountains, how they are firmly set up"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "and on the earth, how it is spread out"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "So, [O Prophet] exhort them: your task is only to exhort"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "you are not their keeper"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "But whoever turns back and denies the truth"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "will be punished by God with the greatest punishment"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "Certainly, it is to Us that they will return"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 88,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "Then, surely, it is for Us to call them to account"
        }
    ]
}